<div class="two_thirds">
  <div class="pushed_content">
    <h1>send us a message</h1>
    Or check out the <a href='faq'>FAQ below</a>

    <%= simple_form_for @contact, :html => {:class => 'form-horizontal' } do |f| %>
      <table class="contact_table"> 
        <tr>
          <td>* Name</td>
          <td><%= f.input :name, required: true, label: false %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>* Email</td>
          <td><%= f.input :email, required: true, label: false %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>* Message</td>
          <td><%= f.input :message, as: :text, required: true, label: false %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2"><%= f.button :submit, 'Send message', class: "btn btn-primary" %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <div class= "hidden">
        <%= f.input :nickname, :hint => 'Leave this field blank!' %>
      </div>
    <% end %><br>

    <div id='faq' class='faq'>
      <h1>frequently asked questions</h1>
      <span>How much do you charge for an event?</span>
      <p class='no-top'>There are so many factors that go into determining the price of an event that we require information before we can provide a quote. Please use the form above.</p>

      <span>How far are you willing to travel?</span>
      <p class='no-top'>Travel costs are part of a price quote when outside the Portland metro area, but Blackbird
      has played events in Cascadia, OR, Skamania, WA, Lincoln City, OR, and are willing to travel.</p>

      <span>Do you provide your own sound system?</span>
      <p class='no-top'>Yes, the band has a high quality sound system as well as a lighting setup. All we need from the venue in order to create an amazing atmosphere is power.</p>

      <span>Can you learn my favorite song?</span>
      <p class='no-top'>With very few exceptions, yes. We take pride in making the event special for you, and always love learning a few of your favorites to help make it memorable!</p>

      <span>Can you provide dinner music as well as dance music?</span>
      <p class='no-top'>Yes, Blackbird can provide both the quieter dinner background music and the energetic dance music for your event!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%= render partial: "layouts/right_third" %>
